@node 5 "Options"


@{u}O p t i o n s@{uu}
   Before  playing,  you  can  select  some thingies. Use UP/DOWN to move
cursor.  Use  LEFT/RIGHT  to  scroll  selected  item. Press FIRE/SPACE to
select a non-scrollable item. 

@{b}Start at level@{ub} (1-XX)          - Select level to start at.

@{b}Animated intro@{ub}                 - See the intro-cartoon.

@{b}Clear hiscores@{ub}                 - Erase all saved hiscores.

@{b}Control:@{ub} (Keyboard/Joystick)   - Select what to guide Bloog with.

@{b}Musicvolume:@{ub} (OFF/1/2/3/4)     - Music volume; 4 is high.


