@node 8 "Control"


@{u}C o n t r o l@{uu}
   You  can  control  the  Bloog-creature  with  a joystick or a keyboard
(read the chapter 'Options'!). If with a keyboard, FIRE is represented by
the SPACE-key and directions by the cursorkeys.

@{b}LEFT@{ub}    - Walk or push a block left.

@{b}RIGHT@{ub}   - Walk or push a block right.

@{b}UP@{ub}      - Walk or push a block up

@{b}DOWN@{ub}    - Walk or push a block down.

@{b}FIRE@{ub}    - Use  a  teleport-heart  (read  the chapter 'Special objects'!).
Bloog will travel in his face-direction untill he hits a wall.

@{b}ESC-key@{ub} - Restart level.

@{b}Q-key@{ub}   - Exit to title


